        <updateDate>2023-06-14T10:27:39Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Federal Death Penalty Abolition Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits the imposition of a death penalty sentence for a violation of federal law.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;It eliminates statutory authority for the death penalty as a sentencing option for federal offenses. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;It also requires a person who was sentenced to death before enactment of this bill to be resentenced.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
